{{Quote|Shame Archmaester Ch'Vyalthan wasn't a better writer.|[[Varys]]|The Prince of Winterfell}}
'''Ch'Vyalthan''', is an unseen character mentioned in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is deceased when the events of the series begin and is not expected to appear. He was an [[Archmaester]] of [[the Citadel]] and the author of the book ''[[An History of the Great Sieges of Westeros]]''.
